# Cursor

This project uses the **Mantle** harness. The canonical agent spec is `AGENTS.md` at the repo root.

Read `AGENTS.md` first. It is self-contained and describes:

- Brain-first lookup (`brain/<scope>/compiled-truth.md` + `timeline.md`)
- Repo brain conventions (four-file scopes, append-only timelines)
- Changelog discipline (`scripts/log-change.sh` after major changes)
- Fat skills, thin harness (procedures live in `skills/`)
- Stack defaults (inherited from `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` if available)

Do not duplicate guidance here. If a Cursor-specific override is ever needed, add it as a separate rule file, not to this one.
